        Create a new gen from a given MPIR-rational ``value``.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: pari(-2/3)
            -2/3
            sage: pari(QQ(42))
            42
            sage: pari(QQ(42)).type()
            't_INT'
            sage: pari(QQ(1/42)).type()
            't_FRAC'

